# WhatsApp AI Safety Nets

When changing buyer AI or property knowledge paths:

```typescript
if (config.features.newFeature === true) {
  // new path
} else {
  // old path — never delete until proven
}
```

- Add flag in `backend/src/config/index.ts` (`FEATURE_*`, default OFF for new behavior)
- Shadow: `FEATURE_SHADOW_MODE=true` + `featureShadow.util.ts` or inline compare + `logger.warn`
- Lead rollout: `featureRollout.util.ts` + `FEATURE_ROLLOUT_PERCENTAGE`
- Tests: unit test for new behavior + entry in `critical-paths.smoke.test.ts`
- Run `npm run smoke` before deploy

Rollback: set flag `false` on Railway — no redeploy needed if env-only.
